        Features
        --------
        
        - One click installation
        
        
        Installation
        ------------
        
        Install lil_url by running:
        
        pip install url_shortener
        
        Contribute
        ----------
        
        - Issue Tracker: https://github.com/omprakash1989/LilUrl/issues
